name: ANXIETY
description:
You know this days when everything around seems like okay, but without any reason you start worrying and have a prediction that something should happened. This feeling inflames nerves and you start crying but no one understand why. 

So this work is about that feeling, because I have stuck in the same situations so many times. And I think a lot of people understand that feeling, so I wanna say that it’s OKAY 🙌🏻
